OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FA Stockport mum and special
OL,7,Feducational needs teacher is taking on
OL,8,Fthe Manchester Marathon in a saree as
OL,9,Fshe bids to break a Guinness World
OL,10,FRecord.
OL,12,FMadhusmita Jena says she wants to
OL,13,Finspire women of all backgrounds to
OL,14,Fexercise, while also raising money for
OL,15,Fa device to help pupils with
OL,16,Fadditional needs at the school where
OL,17,Fshe works.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FMadhusmita said: "My initial
OL,7,Fmotivation for running in a saree was
OL,8,Fto represent Indian culture and
OL,9,Fheritage, but it's since blossomed
OL,10,Finto promoting how women can run in
OL,11,Fwhatever makes them feel most
OL,12,Fcomfortable."
OL,14,FThe 46-year-old, who was born in
OL,15,FEngland and has lived in countries
OL,16,Fincluding Saudi Arabia, Dubai and
OL,17,FBahrain, says her latest challenge is
OL,18,Fabout representation as much as
OL,19,Frunning.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FShe has already completed several
OL,7,Fmarathons in a saree, with her fastest
OL,8,Ftime coming in Berlin last year, and
OL,9,Fwill now need to go even quicker to
OL,10,Fbeat the current record.
OL,12,FMadhusmita first took up running after
OL,13,Fjoining a marathon training group in
OL,14,FDubai when her eldest son was just
OL,15,Fthree months old.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,F"When I had my first child, I found
OL,7,Fthat I spent a lot of time indoors,
OL,8,Fand so I started running to get out of
OL,9,Fthe house. I actually found giving
OL,10,Fmyself time to do something I enjoy
OL,11,Fhelped me be a better mother."
OL,13,FSeven months later, Madhustmita found
OL,14,Fherself participating in her first
OL,15,Fever marathon at the age of 29 in
OL,16,FDubai, completing it in a time of 3
OL,17,Fhours and 49 minutes.
OL,19,FShe says it quickly became a way of
OL,20,Ffinding time for herself and helped
OL,21,Fher feel better as a mother.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FMadhusmita has been a champion for
OL,7,Fwomen throughout her running journey,
OL,8,Fadvocating for women wearing hijabs to
OL,9,Frun in Egypt, and this inspired 'saree
OL,10,Fruns' in villages in India.
OL,12,FShe hopes that by attempting this
OL,13,FGuinness World Record, she can prove
OL,14,Fthat running can be done in any type
OL,15,Fof clothing.
OL,17,FMadhusmita added: "Achieving this
OL,18,Frecord in England would give me the
OL,19,Fplatform to show British Asians, and
OL,20,Fby extension, women globally just what
OL,21,Fthey can achieve for themselves."
OL,26,@yD@SOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FThe 46-year-old has run three full and
OL,7,Ftwo half marathons in the traditional
OL,8,FSouth Asian garment, with her fastest
OL,9,Ftime being 4 hours and 18 minutes in
OL,10,Fthe 2024 Berlin Marathon.
OL,12,FShe will have to shave off almost half
OL,13,Fan hour to achieve the Guinness World
OL,14,FRecord.
OL,16,FShe has adapted the way she drapes the
OL,17,Fsix-yard saree so it does not catch on
OL,18,Fher feet when running and uses a more
OL,19,Flight weight material.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FNow she is balancing training around
OL,7,Fwork, family life and the effects of
OL,8,Fperi-menopause, affecting her energy
OL,9,Flevels.
OL,11,FShe has adapted her training style by
OL,12,Fdoing interval training over tempo
OL,13,Fruns.
OL,15,FAs a busy working mum, she finds that
OL,16,Fa mix of early morning running, cross-
OL,17,Ftraining, or weight training helps her
OL,18,Fprepare for the endurance races.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776600665
OL,3,CSaree sprinter bids for world marathon
OL,4,Crecord
OL,6,FAlongside the record attempt, she is
OL,7,Ffundraising for an 'eye-gaze device'
OL,8,Ffor Heaton School in Stockport, which
OL,9,Fhelps individuals with additional
OL,10,Fneeds control a computer screen with
OL,11,Ftheir eye movement.
OL,13,FShe commented that it would "be life-
OL,14,Fchanging for pupils with Cerebral
OL,15,FPalsy".
OL,26,@uD@]OUwD@FO]
